{
  "id": "RAW_a569b5d3",
  "title": "“一连串的停机事故，包括与使用 AI 编程工具有关的事件”，如期而至",
  "url": "https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/a-spate-of-outages-including-incidents",
  "date": "2026-03-10 15:24:15",
  "author": "Gary Marcus",
  "siteName": "Marcus on AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\">\n   <p><span>Remember how I warned you a year ago </span><a href=\"https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/decoding-and-debunking-hard-forks\" rel=\"\">that maintaining GenAI code would be harder than writing code</a><span> with GenAI?</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p>Any coder with any chops at all knows that is one thing to write code, and another to debug it (and still another to maintain it, a year or a decade later, which is even harder)</p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p>And remember how Nathan Hamiel and I warned you in August that</p>\n   <div data-component-name=\"DigestPostEmbed\" class=\"digestPostEmbed-flwiST\">\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-reset bg-tertiary-CPDeXV pc-borderRadius-md videoEmbedPlaceholder-AnM6Oo\">\n     <div aria-valuemax=\"100\" aria-valuemin=\"0\" role=\"progressbar\" data-state=\"indeterminate\" data-max=\"100\" aria-label=\"Loading\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-padding-16 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG spinner-q_nGBK theme_default-qMdqgV\">\n      <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" vector-effect=\"non-scaling-stroke\" data-state=\"indeterminate\" data-max=\"100\">\n       <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"var(--color-utility-detail)\" class=\"bg-UXIMqb\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" class=\"fg-MeJce5\"></circle>\n      </svg>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>Right on cue, big problems have indeed started to arrive. FT just </span><a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/7cab4ec7-4712-4137-b602-119a44f771de\" rel=\"\">reported that</a><span> “Amazon holds engineering meeting following AI-related outages”:</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/48187664-9d0a-41ef-435b-af0feaf3b900/public\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset can-restack\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260310223356_0b7edc9f-eb35-479e-8578-ae67ee9a78b5_1095x654.jpeg 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260310223356_0b7edc9f-eb35-479e-8578-ae67ee9a78b5_1095x654.jpeg 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260310223356_0b7edc9f-eb35-479e-8578-ae67ee9a78b5_1095x654.jpeg 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/adc4c976-458d-40da-067d-a4f9d0683a00/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260310223356_0b7edc9f-eb35-479e-8578-ae67ee9a78b5_1095x654.jpeg\" width=\"1095\" height=\"654\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0b7edc9f-eb35-479e-8578-ae67ee9a78b5_1095x654.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:654,&quot;width&quot;:1095,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:173921,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/190514659?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5ad841da-7db7-4af9-a19f-ed5192322d56_1332x1571.jpeg&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1a537b42-0c2b-4a5e-032d-aa1c7323e800/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cc7d9bc9-7ae6-4c24-5e44-a7c266fe7400/public 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260310223356_0b7edc9f-eb35-479e-8578-ae67ee9a78b5_1095x654.jpeg 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260310223356_0b7edc9f-eb35-479e-8578-ae67ee9a78b5_1095x654.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n     <figcaption class=\"image-caption\">\n      <span>H/t Lukasz Olejnik, whose highlighted screen capture I reprint. </span><a href=\"https://x.com/elonmusk/status/2031352859846148366?s=61\" rel=\"\">Elon Musk himself took note</a>\n     </figcaption>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>§</p>\n   <p>A new study from NYU and Alibaba reports similar observations in a new benchmark that focuses on long-term maintainability:</p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!iK9x!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F54e27f44-5c46-40e5-8bf1-b794a64cedbe_1071x1251.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset can-restack\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260310223356_54e27f44-5c46-40e5-8bf1-b794a64cedbe_1071x1251.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260310223356_54e27f44-5c46-40e5-8bf1-b794a64cedbe_1071x1251.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260310223356_54e27f44-5c46-40e5-8bf1-b794a64cedbe_1071x1251.png 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c1f52e2a-2cab-497c-e346-5b8d31491500/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e63db791-a0af-4e0d-6710-7fe5c7da3700/public\" width=\"1071\" height=\"1251\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/54e27f44-5c46-40e5-8bf1-b794a64cedbe_1071x1251.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1251,&quot;width&quot;:1071,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:593005,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/190514659?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F54e27f44-5c46-40e5-8bf1-b794a64cedbe_1071x1251.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260310223356_54e27f44-5c46-40e5-8bf1-b794a64cedbe_1071x1251.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260310223356_54e27f44-5c46-40e5-8bf1-b794a64cedbe_1071x1251.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260310223356_54e27f44-5c46-40e5-8bf1-b794a64cedbe_1071x1251.png 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e63db791-a0af-4e0d-6710-7fe5c7da3700/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>As Chris Laub summarized the study on X,</p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p>Alibaba tested 18 AI coding agents on 100 real codebases, spanning 233 days each. they failed spectacularly. [It] turns out passing tests once is easy. maintaining code for 8 months without breaking everything is where AI completely collapses.</p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p>In fairness, some of the latest systems have done better than earlier ones, but for mission critical systems, even a small number of errors can be deadly. As Amazon is discovering in the real-world.</p>\n   <p>We may well move to a regime in which AI writes most code — but for a long time to come we are going to need humans to fix the mess.</p>\n   <p></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Gary Marcus 强调了亚马逊近期发生的与 AI 相关的停机事故以及一项新研究，旨在论证虽然 AI 可以生成代码，但在长期维护和可靠性方面表现极差。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Gary Marcus 强调了亚马逊近期发生的与 AI 相关的停机事故以及一项新研究，旨在论证虽然 AI 可以生成代码，但在长期维护和可靠性方面表现极差。",
  "summary": "本文是对软件工程中生成式 AI 隐藏成本的警示性评论。Marcus 引用了《金融时报》关于亚马逊因 AI 相关停机事故而触发工程会议的报道，暗示 AI 编程的“速度”是以牺牲稳定性为代价的。他进一步引用了纽约大学和阿里巴巴的一项基准研究，该研究在 233 天的时间里测试了 18 个 AI 编程智能体，发现虽然这些智能体可以通过初始测试，但随着时间的推移，它们无法在不引起系统性破坏的情况下维护代码库。核心信息是，在任务关键型环境中，人类的监督对于管理 AI 生成代码引入的技术债和错误仍然不可或缺。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 生成的代码在长期维护方面面临的挑战远高于初始代码生成。",
      "explanation": "虽然 AI 可以快速生成功能代码片段，但在数月或数年内调试和维护这些代码的复杂性仍然是一项以人为核心的任务，AI 目前难以有效处理。"
    },
    {
      "point": "现实世界中的生产停机事故正越来越多地与盲目使用 AI 编程助手联系在一起。",
      "explanation": "亚马逊等大公司的工程危机报告表明，AI 工具引入的错误可能导致任务关键型故障，从而需要紧急的人为干预和流程重新评估。"
    },
    {
      "point": "长期基准测试显示，当 AI 智能体被要求长期维护代码库时，它们会陷入崩溃。",
      "explanation": "一项涉及 100 个真实代码库的研究表明，AI 智能体在 8 个月的时间窗口内无法维持代码完整性，这证明通过单次测试并不代表软件的长期健康。"
    },
    {
      "point": "在可预见的 AI 辅助编程未来中，人类的专业知识是必不可少的安全网。",
      "explanation": "即使 AI 逐渐开始编写大部分原始代码，人类开发者的角色也会转向高风险的编辑和调试员，必须收拾自动化工具留下的“烂摊子”。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "任何有实力的程序员都知道，写代码是一回事，调试代码是另一回事（而一年或十年后维护代码则更难，甚至更辛苦）。",
    "在不破坏一切的情况下维护代码 8 个月，是 AI 完全崩溃的地方。",
    "对于任务关键型系统，即使是少量的错误也可能是致命的。正如亚马逊在现实世界中所发现的那样。",
    "我们很可能会进入一个 AI 编写大部分代码的时代——但在未来很长一段时间内，我们都需要人类来收拾残局。"
  ],
